---
title: Veggie Gyro Wrap with Beyond Meat®, Fries and Chopped Salad
description: This classic gyro wrap is as tasty as it is colourful! Our shawarma spice blend is smoky, sweet and oh-so-delicious. Paired with crunchy cucumber and drizzled with tangy yogurt chili dressing, dinner tonight hits all the high notes!
